```plantuml
@startuml gcba-iris_iris
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "CLI" as CLI {
  rectangle "bin/iris.js" as irisCLI
}

rectangle "Core Components" {
  rectangle "Dispatcher" as Dispatcher #lightblue
  rectangle "Dock" as Dock #lightgreen
  rectangle "Handler" as Handler #lightyellow
  rectangle "Hook" as Hook #lightpink
  rectangle "Flow" as Flow #lightgray
}

rectangle "Infrastructure" {
  rectangle "Thread Pool" as ThreadPool #lightcoral
  rectangle "Logger" as Logger #lightsteelblue
  rectangle "Validator" as Validator #lightgoldenrodyellow
}

User --> irisCLI : execute command

irisCLI --> Dispatcher : initialize, register flows
Dispatcher --> Dock : route message
Dispatcher --> Handler : process message
Dispatcher --> Hook : pre/post processing
Dock --> Dispatcher : receive/parse message
Handler --> Dispatcher : generate response
Hook --> Dispatcher : execute custom logic

Dispatcher --> ThreadPool : manage threads
Dispatcher --> Logger : log events
Dispatcher --> Validator : validate configuration

@enduml
```